{
  "stem": "13141.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course, they came when [LAUGHS] the synagogue was burned down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there wasn't much standing there anymore when I got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was pretty much burned out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was burning a-- it was just a, a, a pile-- a pile of rubble.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just some of the, the outer parts were still standing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how did you know it was happening?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or what, what brought--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was the next day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was now November 10th, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they, they-- I mean, if you read the paper, and when you-- they, they, they said that German-- the German hate for the Jews brought this about.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it-- of, of course, it was all an organized-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was organized beforehand, very well organized, because it was done all over Germany at the same time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they smashed the windows of all Jewish shops.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, a lot was-- of the merchandise was plundered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took-- the next day and during that particular night, they took-- all Jewish men, they took to Dachau, which was a concentration camp near Munich.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some people, they never got out of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those who got out of Dachau were told-- and I know this from my uncle, who had been in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was not in Dachau because they did not-- they did not take any-- anyone below the age of 18.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when my uncle came back about two or three months after November-- it must have been January or February of, of 1939-- he told me that they were told-- and they had to sign.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were told by the Germans there-- and they had to sign the corresponding papers that they will try their best to get out of Germany, to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
